author: @hnnhnn0
text: I have so many reasons why I adore Liz and consider her my ultimate bias in IVE. First off, it’s obvious that she’s stunning, and she really rocks that hair color. But her beauty is just the surface. I liked her from the beginning because of her incredible vocals, her voice is truly beautiful. What makes her even more special is that she’s not just talented and gorgeous, but also incredibly kind-hearted. I remember watching a prank video where a staff member dropped a cake and asked Liz to cover for them. Surprisingly, Liz agreed, even hiding it from her IVE members so the staff wouldn’t get in trouble. When they revealed it was a prank, she was so emotional and started crying, I’ve never seen such pure innocence. That moment really touched me and completely won me over. It’s rare to find someone so genuine and pure, and I really hope she stays this way, don’t change. We need more people like her in the world. I don’t usually write comments like this, but I just wanted to say that I’ll always support her. She has my utmost respect. And by the way, I’m older, so unnie support all the way ❤ Good Job for the release of Attitude
